snippet.title: Hydorah Trailer
snippet.description:
This is the official trailer for Hydorah, a free indie game that features lots of short and intense levels, unlockable weapons, secrets and a large library of enemies and bosses.

+info and downloads: http://www.locomalito.com/juegos_hydorah.php
